io.confluent.ksql.physical.pull

Class PullPhysicalPlanBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.physical.pull.PullPhysicalPlanBuilder

  • public class PullPhysicalPlanBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Traverses the logical plan top-down and creates a physical plan for pull queries. The pull query must access a table that is materialized in a state store. The logical plan should consist of Project, Filter and DataSource nodes only.
